cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid_verbosity' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid_verbosity' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid_verbosity' 會導致配置解析失敗，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
